        <h2>Rules for Posting Comments on Moview</h2>
        <p>
            When posting comments on Moview, please adhere to the following rules:
        </p>
        <ul>
            <li>Do not use profanity, hate speech, racial slurs, or insults.</li>
            <li>Ensure proper grammar and punctuation in your comments.</li>
            <li>Do not use imperative language or make demands as if you were a paying customer.</li>
            <li>Comments containing spoilers must use the "Spoiler" button; otherwise, they will not be approved.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Where Are the Subtitles?</h2>
        <p>
            We understand that subtitles are essential for an enjoyable movie-watching experience. Here's what you need to know about subtitles on Moview:
        </p>
        <ul>
            <li>Subtitles are provided for movies with available English subtitle sources.</li>
            <li>The availability of subtitles depends on the availability of English subtitle sources, and their release schedule is unpredictable.</li>
            <li>If we have two or more translators actively working on a movie, rest assured that Moview will be the first to release English subtitles.</li>
        </ul>

